{"tid":878196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保險界陳健波：現時不填海將對不起下一代  耗盡庫戶1兆複雜項目亦可短時間表決","createTime":"2018-10-27T02:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T11:25:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e9daa4fe06fc4827bbb9f26ac6dfa6ca262e6a","tid":878196,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425127-20181027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425127-20181027.htm&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2ugtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a864020a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425127-20181027.htm&h=97c97352\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425127-20181027.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會保險界議員陳健波說，本港所有問題都與房屋有關，反對人士提出的方法例如使用棕地，以往英國人都處理不到，特首林鄭月娥曾擔任發展局局長亦認為是此路不通。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波出席一個電台節目時指出，公眾就填海造地問題不要只考慮風險，認為現時不填海會對不起下一代，反對者一定會是歷史罪人。<br />\n<br />\n立法會工程界議員盧偉國在同一節目表示，本港開埠以來大幅填海，而過去多年本港停止造地，認為現時要急起直追，他指出利用填海可造出更多土地變成新的核心區，認為要思考香港長遠發展規劃。盧偉國表示，若指氣候變化會帶來水位升高的問題，工程角度上並非不可解決，認為外界是過份顧慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425132-20181027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425132-20181027.htm&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2ugtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=fb3003a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425132-20181027.htm&h=8c35293f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425132-20181027.htm</a><br />\n立法會財委會主席陳健波在一個電台節目談及當局的填海計劃時表示，以前政府較為懦弱，遇到反對就會調整項目排在後面，但他說財委會已修改會議程序，就算複雜問題都可以短時間內表決，相信最多用10幾小時便可完成處理。陳健波說，若可行性研究都不做，就解決不到市民的擔心。<br />\n<br />\n另外，公民黨議員郭家麒表示，政府未提及明日大嶼計劃前，指香港欠1200公頃土地，當中房屋範疇欠缺的土地有230公頃，根據學者研究，香港有三成土地是未規劃及使用。他批評當局，不按土地收回條例，收回土地作公共用途。"},{"pid":"a48c3701a321fb9f7306ee112b3af7f249334fc4","tid":878196,"uid":25250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"你地根本就唔想香港人生下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca3931eb73234417b282b3ead98c26e4c85528f","tid":878196,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a48c3701a321fb9f7306ee112b3af7f249334fc4","tid":878196,"uid":25250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"你地根本就唔想香港人生下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"新移蝗既下一代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a145a941b381808361e9e1c51c09d16fda2f71c3","tid":878196,"uid":126283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"保險狗講咩都唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3955ea2dd642cff56d46a341c6bb9355c28519b7","tid":878196,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"工程爛尾超支與否都唔關佢同中共事，到時幫中國洗劫香港所有嘅儲備就得。"},{"pid":"b2ecdebbed7b526ca68be4a45ea343796d14b400","tid":878196,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a145a941b381808361e9e1c51c09d16fda2f71c3","tid":878196,"uid":126283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"保險狗講咩都唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:28:05.000Z","msg":"既然保險界陳健波咁講<br />\n<br />\n其實應該由全港保險公司出錢啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地夠錢比"},{"pid":"8367b3bf86a6609874d2d640f6bbbc04f1138889","tid":878196,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e29129174278c3d9c27551fed61a2b00804b52","tid":878196,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"陳健波個 Associate of The Chartered Insurance I